  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Clown House</strong> is a short, unique horror experience.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You must find the key to escape from the Clown House. Some of the residents are harmless, some of them are not. You carry a gun, but you can't know which clowns are willing to harm you unless they start to attack.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Worst part? Killing an innocent clown turns you into one of them.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
